				["description"] = "|cFFFFFFFFStep 4:|r The next |cFFFFD700Inconspicuous Note|r will spawn on the table.  Click this to continue.  The note reads...\r\r|cFFFFFFFFDeeper than deep.|r\r|cFFFFFFFFAwaits your seat.|r",
